{"tid":47520,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(有透)呢到有冇手足有追開魔禁小說/魔禁迷","createTime":"2016-12-20T11:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T11:35:30.000Z","uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b31fbf6614495397068163d379f1daff35d5dfe3","tid":47520,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:41:15.000Z","msg":"舊約既暗部大戰 一方對老二<br />\n英國王女叛變篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第三次世界大戰篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n河馬全盛時期最好睇始終都係新約當麻對女魔神(新約9-10)<br />\n既悲慘 黑暗 到熱血 去到最後最後既悲壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比女魔神用各種方法殺過萬次 再復活再殺 <br />\n就係為左逼當麻自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n崩潰而打算決定自殺既當麻既最後一句對白長達四頁堪稱經典<br />\n第九卷插圖連精華:<a href=\"https://disp.cc/b/21-7a3i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisp.cc%2Fb%2F21-7a3i&d=YHB6s8ga2I4eb32L6MIQwEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3bf402a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://disp.cc/b/21-7a3i</a><br />\n<br />\n最後女魔神為左當麻既世界放棄自己既世界<br />\n放棄抵抗甘願被全世界圍剿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後當麻決定與全世界(上條勢力)為敵<br />\n 出現全劇最型插圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/193028_6d9ff07f234cdc773c8a41620d066e13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F193028_6d9ff07f234cdc773c8a41620d066e13.jpg&h=321eac0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到另一個高潮：2人VS60億人<br />\n宗教魔法側科學側美國全部落order要擊殺呢兩個人<br />\n呢一卷打曬所有基本上有名既聖人能力者魔法側高手甚至打埋index<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有一方專登放水笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢章最後以一個好悲壯形式完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後開始寫好多美琴同食蜂女王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而當麻脾氣越黎越差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5bf18d53b7b318d95de3b5f5cc75f080bf3413","tid":47520,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"我覺得依套野比你燈死左"},{"pid":"274f1b74f14595a7a9a051be9ce3a8418109d509","tid":47520,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得依套野比你燈死左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅到依家仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十年有多啦"},{"pid":"e9e3e440039d2f6f14a23b227578710a832bc0d9","tid":47520,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"茅"},{"pid":"57422f0deae817dc2b5d0863618457d93f6e9186","tid":47520,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6ebaf904a7504139e5eafa451ae85cded7a39560","tid":47520,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"當麻好撚趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想打鳩佢"},{"pid":"f01bb73d5f1ae57ef7aca7909ceb74ac1475a2b1","tid":47520,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茅</blockquote><br />\n茅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3115e8baf2800423edb6c8f4b526d5aa4ccf86f6","tid":47520,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當麻好撚趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想打鳩佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主角威能太強"},{"pid":"587f471568a43b6b60000a4fbfa969c6e27480f0","tid":47520,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b3d73de64f1136596f68255f63fac31018b69e","tid":47520,"uid":30256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"index<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e7c1c7ebfdb1c487502da9c3af3e6b32af21cc","tid":47520,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當麻好撚趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想打鳩佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主角威能太強</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係因為當麻先會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢表面威能 但其實真係好撚慘<br />\n小說後面有講 d遭遇係慘到冇得再慘<br />\n<br />\n我記得有幅圖 係個圖表<br />\n講一堆唔同角色既悲慘程度<br />\n整圖條友擺當麻係個圖表出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c68fd4aba2e9713f0194c4ac2fd5b6d1fdfd54","tid":47520,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"講下有幾慘 動話完左無睇過"},{"pid":"1b74fa64a9b7bcf5f6f35261aa95095d34c28514","tid":47520,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下有幾慘 動話完左無睇過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三言兩語好難令你感受到有幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63b2a4d884a169e91ffe0e09ab60924edf0672a","tid":47520,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:35:34.000Z","msg":"我只睇左動畫，覺得佢好撚乞人憎好離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎呢種基拉大和式既人物，唔係有主角威能保護應該死左好耐"},{"pid":"3506af1ec0bce50cf27616a633186237a2196590","tid":47520,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"當麻同果d天跌落黎既外掛主角好唔同<br />\n<br />\n靠自己同班手足一齊打生打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係點拎到2017這本輕小說真厲害! 男性榜第一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一定既個人魅力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa62f643c902c4b805f1dc092f645097b9befba","tid":47520,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只睇左動畫，覺得佢好撚乞人憎好離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎呢種基拉大和式既人物，唔係有主角威能保護應該死左好耐</blockquote><br />\n基拉係打柒人地  當麻係比人打柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3165ffd61353625bd10986cc1aa975d59e6834a9","tid":47520,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只睇左動畫，覺得佢好撚乞人憎好離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最憎呢種基拉大和式既人物，唔係有主角威能保護應該死左好耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得幾貼地 d性格似中學生<br />\n會撩下女 會9up<br />\n<br />\n而且唔係唔會死 而係科學側班醫生醫術高明姐<br />\n有人統計過佢幾多次重傷入醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且佢好過基拉好多"},{"pid":"6d95ff9cefcb91d417de2792a61ae0efa4175d38","tid":47520,"uid":54904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:35:30.000Z","msg":"之前睇動畫果時好迷呢套<br />\n跟住買左講世界大戰戈幾本小說到依家都未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇心機睇<br />\n同埋覺得一方呢個角色真係好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}